{"id": "1519934840626221056", "channel_id": "1519932722548703242", "author_id": "214749389632176129", "author_name": "kevsalvador", "content": "General tips:\n- double burial grounds covenant is a good build to survive.\n\nWave 1:\nCore Awakers: Caecus and Nautila\nTips:\n- prioritize Caecus exalt to increase counter\n- rouse Caecus or Naut when boss doesn't intent to attack.\n- posse only when boss intends to attack\n\nWave 1 Extra:\nCore awaker: Ghelot\nTips:\n- Dupe Ghelot's 4 cost with posse.\n- use Salvador to turn Furnace into shield. It provides more value than healing. Unless u have Bleed on ur team.\n- before using your ghelot 4 costs, exalt Salvador or Helot.\n- Rouse Ghelot for dmg scaling", "timestamp": "2026-06-26T05:18:25.029000+00:00", "thread_id": "1519932722548703242", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-26T05:37:54.349000+00:00"}
