{"id": "1519937372421099592", "channel_id": "1519932722548703242", "author_id": "214749389632176129", "author_name": "kevsalvador", "content": "Wave 2:\nCore Awakers: Xu and Gdoll\nTips:\n- Gdoll OE is ideal but her Illusion's end is still very useful to cut down the boss.\n- Rouse Xu. It's always worth it.\n- GDoll E1 at least to get the weakness proc.\n- Nymph is an okay weakness applier if ur desperate. You can also use Faint devour.\n- Xu E3 recommended to get more spellbound stacks.\n\nWave 2 Extra:\nCore: Mouchette and Sanga\nTips:\n- this wasn't an ideal Mouchette team bc Sanga performed too well\n- Sanga has an excellent image relic. All her cards get Prepare. I suggest playing her cards last. Only when u have arith left.\n- Rouse Mouchette.", "timestamp": "2026-06-26T05:28:28.656000+00:00", "thread_id": "1519932722548703242", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-26T05:37:35.988000+00:00"}
