{"id": "1519941373493645332", "channel_id": "1519932722548703242", "author_id": "214749389632176129", "author_name": "kevsalvador", "content": "Wave 3 Extra:\nCore: Pollux and Castor\n-  E1 Pollux and E1 Castor is good to start scaling Pollux\n- leap card > sacred heart > plume > sacred > annihilation > sacred to get a lot of sin marks\n- prioritize exalting Pollux and using up all his sacred hearts in one turn.\n- splashing a Caro awaker gives you embryos to exalt Pollux faster\n- Rouse Pollux to get his exalt faster\n- Arachne isn't ideal in this team bc your annihilation is on cooldown", "timestamp": "2026-06-26T05:44:22.586000+00:00", "thread_id": "1519932722548703242", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-26T05:45:47.205000+00:00"}
