{"id": "1519943180567445565", "channel_id": "1519932722548703242", "author_id": "214749389632176129", "author_name": "kevsalvador", "content": "Wave 4:\nCore: Vortice\nTips:\n- vortice image relic is good bc you get more Reload stacks from one Reload card.\n- prioritize exalting other awakers. Ideally ones with 100 aliemus exalts. Not 200 aliemus like Saya.\n- splash Caro is good for embryo to exalt Corpo and Murphy faster.\n- Red stance is good when you wanna exalt Vortice", "timestamp": "2026-06-26T05:51:33.426000+00:00", "thread_id": "1519932722548703242"}
{"id": "1519955194052481074", "channel_id": "1519932722548703242", "author_id": "214749389632176129", "author_name": "kevsalvador", "content": "Wave 5:\nCore: Gmurphy\n- I prefer playing this team with Tulu but I changed it to Winkle to get more Weakness proc and charge up Gmurphy faster.\n- Ideal burst turn: Red stance > Miryam 0-cost Rouse > Tulu exalt > Gmurphy oe> Murphy Waltz> murphy 0- cost > fish for more Murphy Waltz > Posse to play more murphy Waltz\n- you can also goli exalt before gmurphy oe if u have enough hand space.", "timestamp": "2026-06-26T06:39:17.664000+00:00", "thread_id": "1519932722548703242", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-26T06:39:36.681000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1519955193783910511", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-26-13-52-42-62_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 179998, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1519932722548703242/1519955193783910511/Screenshot_2026-06-26-13-52-42-62_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=6a4018d5&is=6a3ec755&hm=eea5fdafdd40a5668cdae699a67dfe9c6e0c42d579b2f66019f90db68d569370&"}]}
